  PreToolUse hooks                                                                                              
  Review new or changed hooks, then turn them on or off.                                                        
                                                                                                                
  [!] Hook 1 · new                                                                                              
                                                                                                                
  Event     PreToolUse                                                                                          
  Matcher   Bash                                                                                                
  Source    User config - /tmp/hooks.json                                                                       
  Command   /tmp/pre-tool-use-check.sh                                                                          
  Timeout   30s                                                                                                 
  Trust     New hook - review required                                                                          
                                                                                                                
  Press t to trust; esc to go back
